**Segments**

The Core HR Software Market can be segmented based on deployment type, organization size, vertical, and region. In terms of deployment type, the market is divided into cloud-based and on-premises solutions. Cloud-based solutions are increasingly popular due to their scalability, flexibility, and cost-effectiveness. Organization size segments include small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) and large enterprises. SMEs are adopting core HR software to streamline their HR processes and improve efficiency. Vertical segmentation covers various industries such as IT and Telecom, BFSI, Healthcare, Retail, Manufacturing, and others. Each industry has unique HR requirements, driving the demand for tailored core HR software solutions. Geographically, the market is segmented into North America, Europe, Asia-Pacific, Latin America, and Middle East & Africa, with North America leading the market due to early adoption of advanced HR technologies.

